-- Brazil's Amorim Says Diplomatic Solution to Iran Nuclear Issue Possible
-- Benjamin Harvey
-- 2010-07-25T08:56:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-25/brazil-s-amorim-says-diplomatic-solution-to-iran-nuclear-issue-possible.html

          
          
             Brazilian Foreign Minister Celso
Amorim said a diplomatic solution to the Iranian nuclear issue
is possible.   
 Amorim spoke in Istanbul today at a joint press conference
with his Turkish counterpart Ahmet Davutoglu.   
 To contact the reporter on this story:
